{"tid":1017190,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"飲酒傾計搵朋友谷(終於開到第三了!)","createTime":"2019-02-11T09:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T09:31:55.000Z","uid":5849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0bdce09136e3d419ad08ee06613963d9f4112021","tid":1017190,"uid":5849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"谷已經開咗差唔多一年啦<br />\n每個星期都會出去一次<br />\n除咗飲酒都會搞下其他活動，打邊爐etc <br />\n但咁當然飲酒多，話明飲酒谷吖ma<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輕輕鬆鬆，On99啱傾就入谷啦<br />\n有控制人數，禁止小圈子<br />\n因為每個會員都可以講野<br />\n男女人數平衡，維持一定人數嘅谷<br />\n啱晒怕羞既你，(絲打既你唔使驚得你一個女<br />\n我哋其中一個谷主都係女)<br />\n<br />\n另外唔似其他谷成百幾二百人，都唔知邊個打邊個<br />\n<br />\n謝絕狗公同無聊人士<br />\n精神不正常，唔該有啲自知之明<br />\n健康飲酒識朋友活動谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外諗清楚先好入谷，有啲入咗完全唔講嘢都唔知做咩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後同大家講聲<br />\n你唔踏出第一步永遠都唔知將來會點<br />\n你入到黎可能開心又可能唔開心<br />\nBut why not try ?<br />\n可能你另外一半就喺度等緊你</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有意者留TG ，又可以pm 我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/whatever8880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwhatever8880&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu18tNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=cc58e05b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/whatever8880</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xaj0j3d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxaj0j3d.png&h=4da71bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CbT8tWz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCbT8tWz.png&h=02814ed6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}